author: @BLACKPINK1Revolution
text: Rosé was just a girl from Australia and look what she become. I have always and will always support her no matter the cost. I have always wanted to talk to Rosé and just tell her about my life and how she has changed it. I know she will never meet me, but I want her to know I got her back even if I am just a 13 year old girl, I want her to know that I understand what she has been through, and its a lot. I am so happy for her that she has made 3 best friends that will stick with her till the end. When Rosé said "So I feel like everybody out there who feels like you're not worth it and cannot get through whatever coming against your dreams, I feel like believing in what you love to do and not forgetting to enjoy yourself is always the best part. Because I feel like anything, any obstacle is breakable. I got your back," this made me cry. No Rosé I got your back no matter the cost! Now I am just a girl from Arizona who has a dream of also becoming a K-POP star, I want to be like you. I want to break my obstacle and make life long lasting friends just like you have. I just don't know if I have what it takes to be one. Constantly my parents and siblings and friends beat me down and tell me that I can't do it, I am not Korean, and I just suck. But like you, I also believe I can break my obstacles. Maybe I won't end up becoming it, but I will do what it takes to try to get there. I love you Rosé you are a big example to me. Please don't forget you are always welcome with me. Welcome home Rosé 🖤💗❤😘

Влады́ко Человеколю́бче, Царю́ веко́в и Пода́телю благи́х, разру́шивший вражды́ средосте́ния и мир пода́вший ро́ду челове́ческому, да́руй и ны́не мир рабо́м Твои́м, вкорени́ в них стра́х Твой и друг к дру́гу любо́вь утверди́: угаси́ вся́ку ра́спрю, отъими́ вся разногла́сия и собла́зны.
